        "message": "Patch Set 2: -Code-Review\n\nMichael, I am sorry for the extra work.   As I said, I should have caught the issue in the first code inspection, so to have had the discussion then instead of now.  I apologize about it.   In any case, I appreciate your good \"citizenship\" and teamwork manners.   Thank you.",
        "patchset_number": 2
